{"tid":2493671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【小學生統治】溫家寶於澳門報章撰文悼念亡母，遭微信封殺無法share","createTime":"2021-04-18T05:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:48:00.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"edcc4327b54032f524dd1176ae172f0d61512bff","tid":2493671,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:48:00.000Z","msg":"篇文由影帝寫，本身已經係啲裝點門面嘅嘢<br />\n結果都係收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/3CNQJHCZQJG43DDYJF3S4NDMYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F3CNQJHCZQJG43DDYJF3S4NDMYE%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=660fcded\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F3CNQJHCZQJG43DDYJF3S4NDMYE%2F&h=2e6a8eee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/3CNQJHCZQJG43DDYJF3S4NDMYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n// 國務院前總理溫家寶的母親於去年12月離世，今年清明節前夕，他撰文追憶亡母，文章於3月25日至4月15日分4篇在《澳門導報》上連載。文章內容講述亡母一生，溫家寶亦在字裏行間抒發家國情懷：「我心目中的中國應該是一個充滿公平正義的國家，那裏永遠有對人心、人道和人的本質的尊重，永遠有青春、自由、奮鬥的氣質。我為此吶喊過、奮鬥過。這是生活讓我懂得的真理，也是媽媽給予的。」溫在當前形勢下作出此番言論，不禁讓人有所聯想。不過，有內地網民指，該文已在微信禁止流傳。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZALy4YwsmNJaBMh288quCNg2dvmEjhtZTyMYAZvWDLfe?filename=7axzJLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7axzJLi.jpg&h=089178e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}